<!DOCTYPE ui:UiBinder SYSTEM "http://dl.google.com/gwt/DTD/xhtml.ent">
<ui:UiBinder xmlns:ui="urn:ui:com.google.gwt.uibinder"
	xmlns:g="urn:import:com.google.gwt.user.client.ui" xmlns:mn='urn:import:mindnotes.client.ui'>
	<ui:style>
		.bordered {
		border: 1px #000 solid;
		}
		.sidebar {
		padding: 12px;
		}
		.sidebar p {
		text-align: justify;
		}

		.header {
		border-bottom: 1px #f00 solid;
		background: #222228;
		margin-bottom: 12px;
		color: #fffaf1;
		height: 60px;
		}

		.header h1 {
		margin-top: 0px;
		}
	</ui:style>
	<g:DockLayoutPanel unit='PX' ui:field="dockLayoutPanel">
		<g:north size='60'>
			<g:DockLayoutPanel unit='PX'>
			<g:center>
				<g:HTML addStyleNames="{style.header}">
					<h1 class="header-h1">Mind Notes App<span style="font-size: smaller">(30.06.2009)</span></h1>
				</g:HTML>
			</g:center>
			<g:east size='120'>
				<g:FlowPanel addStyleNames="{style.header}">
					<g:Button ui:field="loadButton">Load from cloud</g:Button>
					<g:Button ui:field="saveButton">Save to cloud</g:Button>
				</g:FlowPanel>
			</g:east>
			</g:DockLayoutPanel>
		</g:north>
		<g:center>
			<mn:MindMapWidget ui:field="mindMapWidget"></mn:MindMapWidget>
		</g:center>
		<g:west size='266'>
			<g:HTML>
				<div class="{style.sidebar}">
					<h2>Iteration 3</h2>
					<p><strong>Cloud Storage</strong></p>
					<ul>
					<li>The nodes are now positioned on an AbsolutePanel, and their positions are calculated
					by the script. Left-hand side and right-hand sides are now supported.</li>
					<li>After adding or deleting nodes, try undoing this (ctrl+z)</li>
					<li>Nodes now can be edited using rich text editing. You can play with the B-I-U buttons, or paste some text from another webpage.</li>
					<li>Try cutting (ctrl+x) and pasting (ctrl+v) nodes around. Copy is not implemented yet.</li>
					<li>I abandoned the idea of porting this to SVG, because current method works well enough.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</g:HTML>
		</g:west>
	</g:DockLayoutPanel>

</ui:UiBinder> 